        Optional list of changes that make up the changeset. Not all events will include this information.

      • getRequests

        List<PulseRequest> getRequests()
        Optional list of requests that the changeset was associated with.
        Returns:
        List of requests. If not available will be null. If the changeset has no associated requests, will be an empty collection.

      • isChainRunContributor

        boolean isChainRunContributor()
        If the changeset if provided as part of a chain event, this flag indicates that the changeset was a contributor to the chain run. If not part of a chain event, the flag is false.
        Returns:
        Indicates changeset contributed to a chain run.
